1) Stop And Wait.pdf contains the report

2) how to run
g++ -o s Sender.cpp
g++ -o c Reciever.cpp

3) Open two terminals
type the name of executable and give the name of required file name as command line parameter. 
for sender give the name of file to sent as command line parameter
for Reciever give the name of file in which you want to recieve. 

4) In first terminal type: ./c recv.pdf
   In second terminal type: ./s file.pdf

   Make sure you execute the reciever first, to get accurate transfer times.